content.title: Test large whitelist of Osmosis tokens - REDUX
content.details:
Follow-up proposal for Polaris integration testing. Also whitelist new native Osmosis token itself, forgot in Prop #80.

The code used to generate the wasm can be found here: https://github.com/namada-net/namada-governance-upgrades/blob/d871e8f516c7563de3dcdfdc1e03b53bf3a9bfae/proposals/testnet/test-polaris-whitelist/src/lib.rs.
